'''''A United Kingdom''''' ni romantic drama film yasohotse muri 2016 muri [[Botswana]] iyoborwa na Amma Asante yanditswe na Guy Hibbert, ishingiye ku urugo nyakuri, ubuzima hagati ya Seretse Khama, kuragwa ubutegetsi kwa Bechuanaland ( yari perezida wa [[Botswana]]),  n'umugore we Ruth Williams Khama .  David Oyelowo na Rosamund Pike bagaragaza Seretse na Ruth.

Yerekanwe mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Toronto mu 2016,  kandi ni yo filime yatangiye iserukiramuco rya sinema rya 60 rya London. 

