== uko yakozwe ==
Pike yinjiye mu bakinnyi muri Gicurasi 2015, Asante yinjira nyuma gato.  Muri Nzeri 2015, Asante yatangaje ko gufata amashusho bizagabanywa hagati ya [[Botswana]] na London, kandi ko bizatangira mu Kwakira mu rwego rwo kwitegura irekurwa rya filimi muri 2016 rihurirana n’imyaka 50 y'ubwigenge muri Botswana. 

Mu Kwakira 2015, Jack Davenport na Tom Felton bifatanije n'aba bakinnyi.  Mu Gushyingo 2015, amashusho amwe yabereye hafi ya Hyde Park / Kensington Gardens harimo na Imperial College Union . Umukinnyi wa sinema yari Sam McCurdy naho umuyobozi wa filimi  yari Simon Bowles . 
